
Introduction
============

SCAP, (Single Cell Analysis Platform), is a mini version of single cell analysis pipeline, and designed for the wet-lab scientists.




Requirements
============

1). Python 2, Python 2.7.x or newer 

2). R version 2.15.1 or higher

	- Rtsne
	- DESeq2
	- edgeR
	- gplots
	- plotrix




How to run ?
============

To run SCAP, go to " %SCAP_HOME/bin/ " folder and double click "scap"

or open the terminal, enter to the directory " %SCAP_HOME/bin/ " and type:

python scap

